      "rdf:value": "<L>8843<pc>47,1<k1>anvADi<k2>anv-ADi<h>2<e>2\r\n<hom>2.</hom> <s>anv-ADi</s> ¦ <lex>m.</lex> repentance, remorse, <ls>L.</ls><info lex=\"m\"/>\r\n<LEND>"
